<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_276_r1l2"><expan>Lıeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> / Wir heten etwas cʒe <expan>werb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> an <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnedıge<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_276_r1l3"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>cʒog</expan> <expan>Frıdr<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Öſterrich / vnd ıſt vns geſagt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_276_r1l4"> <expan>word<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / wie er 
<del rend="strikethrough">in der </del> <expan>yecʒunde<ex>n</ex></expan> in der gegend vmb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_276_r1l5">ewch ſeÿ / . <expan>Davo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / . Ob Jr ıht weſt <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>ervare<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_276_r1l6">möcht wo man ſein gnade cʒüm nechſten treffen <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒü </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_276_r1l7">Jm <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> möcht / daʒ Jr vns das an <expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan> briefe wiſſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_276_r1l8">laſſen wöllet / . vnd ob Jr auch ſüſt von den lewffen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_276_r1l9">yecʒunden iht newes weſt / das ew füglıch <expan>w<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒü <expan>ſchreıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_276_r1l10">daʒ Jr vns das auch <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrıbt</expan> bey <expan>dıſe<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>bot<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_276_r1l11">Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir vmb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> erſamkeıt in <expan>ſölıche<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_276_r1l12">ſachen mit vvıllen allcʒeit <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> <expan>verdıene<ex>n</ex></expan> / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>Sabb<ex>at</ex>o</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_276_line_1576576773188_1372"><expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> <expan>Bonifacij</expan> </ab>
</div>
<div type="cedula"><ab facs="#facs_276_r1l14">Cedula </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_276_r1l15">Auch <expan>lıeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> frewnde <expan>het<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir den <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>Rege<ex>n</ex>ſp<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> <expan>geſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / vnd die <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_276_r1l16">vns <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>geſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / wie 
<add><ab facs="#facs_276_line_1576576786148_1385">Jn </ab></add> Stephan <expan>Bertholtſhof<ex>er</ex></expan> einen gelawbſbrief </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_276_r1l17">braht hab <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>gnedıg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> künig von <expan>Vng<ex>er</ex>n</expan> / vnd hab dar </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_276_r1l18">auf <expan>geworb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / daʒ ſie Jn durch Jr Stat <expan>laſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> cʒıehen / das wöll er </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_276_r1l19">tün on Jr ſcheden / Aber wo er ſeÿ <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> auf welıche cʒeit er <expan>köme<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_276_r1l20">ſüll / des <expan>wiſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> ſie noch kein aigenſchaft / . Auch ıſt vns geſagt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_276_r1l21">wie derſelb vnſer <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> künig <expan>etlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>fürſte<ex>n</ex></expan> vmb vns ge </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_276_line_1576576828276_1406"><expan>ſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hab / daʒ ſie bey Jm ſein ſüllen auf <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_276_r1l24">leıchnams tage cʒü frankfurt / . Aber wir <expan>künne<ex>n</ex></expan> noch kein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_276_r1l25"><expan>eige<ex>n</ex>ſchaft</expan> ervaren / daʒ er ſıch <expan>erhab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> gen wienn <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_276_r1l26">verrer herauf <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> ſeÿ / So <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir etwen an <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> Reyn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_276_r1l27">gehabt / <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> vns ſagt Er hab <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Meincʒ Reten </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_276_r1l28"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan> / daʒ <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> tag cʒü <expan>frankf<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> erlengt ſüll ſein Acht tag </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_276_r1l29">nach <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> leıchnams tage </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_276" id="137v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Ulme </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, wir heten etwas cze
                            <expan>werb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> an <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnedige<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>czog</expan>
<expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Österrich, und ist uns gesagt
                                <expan>word<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, wie er
                            <expan>yeczunde<ex>n</ex></expan> in der gegend umb ewch sey.
                                <expan>Davo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, ob ir iht west <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ervare<ex>n</ex></expan> möcht, wo man sein gnade czüm nechsten
                        treffen <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> czü im <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        möcht, daz ir uns das an <expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan> briefe wissen lassen
                        wöllet, und ob ir auch süst von den lewffen yeczunden iht newes west, das ew
                        füglich <expan>w<ex>er</ex></expan> czü <expan>schreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>,
                        daz ir uns das auch <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schribt</expan> bey
                                <expan>dise<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>bot<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir umb
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> ersamkeit in
                            <expan>söliche<ex>n</ex></expan> und <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        sachen mit willen allczeit <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>
<expan>verdiene<ex>n</ex></expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sabb<ex>at</ex>o</expan>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
<expan>Bonifacii.</expan></ab>
</div>
<div type="cedula">
<ab>Cedula. Auch <expan>lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> frewnde,
                            <expan>het<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir den <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Rege<ex>n</ex>sp<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
<expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und die <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> uns
                                <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, wie <add>in</add> Stephan
                                <expan>Bertholtshof<ex>er</ex></expan> einen gelawbsbrief braht hab
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> künig von
                                <expan>Ung<ex>er</ex>n,</expan> und hab darauf
                                <expan>geworb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz sie in durch ir stat
                                <expan>lasse<ex>n</ex></expan> cziehen, das wöll er tün on ir
                        scheden, aber wo er sey <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> auf weliche czeit er
                                <expan>köme<ex>n</ex></expan> süll, des
                            <expan>wisse<ex>n</ex></expan> sie noch kein aigenschaft. Auch ist uns
                        gesagt, wie derselb unser <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>,
                            <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> künig, <expan>etlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürste<ex>n</ex></expan> umb uns ge <expan>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        hab, daz sie bey im sein süllen <app>
<note><q type="date">auf <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> leichnams
                                tage</q>11.06.1411</note>
</app> czü Frankfurt. Aber wir <expan>künne<ex>n</ex></expan> noch kein
                                <expan>eige<ex>n</ex>schaft</expan> ervaren, daz er sich
                                <expan>erhab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> gen Wienn <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> verrer
                        herauf <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> sey, so <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        wir etwen an <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> Reyn gehabt,
                            <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> uns sagt, er hab <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Meincz reten
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz
                            <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> tag czü <expan>Frankf<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
                        erlengt süll sein acht tag nach <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> leichnams tage.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
